        <ol>
            <li><strong>One-to-One Relationships:</strong> How to connect two tables where each record connects to exactly one other record</li>
            <li><strong>One-to-Many Relationships:</strong> The most common relationship type - how one record connects to many others</li>
            <li><strong>Many-to-Many Relationships:</strong> How to handle complex connections between tables</li>
            <li><strong>Practical Examples:</strong> Real code examples you can understand and use</li>
        </ol>
        
        <p>Each lesson will include simple C# code examples that show how to create and use these relationships in your applications.</p>
    </div>

